WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:03:10.680 --> 00:03:13.159
You came here after
defeating many enemies.

3
00:03:13.320 --> 00:03:16.759
May your black steel sword
never get harmed when you fight.

4
00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:20.279
You came after
conquering many castles.

5
00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:23.759
May your spear never
break when you fight.

6
00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:27.719
May your gray horse
never stumble when you run.

7
00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:32.439
May our Allah never let
you need dishonest men.

8
00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:38.159
May you always keep your
faith (imaan) strong

9
00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:42.319
Do you know why they
built the Great Wall of China?

10
00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:47.599
So that the valiant Turks
would pass it. my Mete Khan.

11
00:03:47.760 --> 00:03:50.319
Why did I open the gates
of the lands of Rumelia?

12
00:03:50.440 --> 00:03:53.919
So your bloodline would grow
with conquests. my Alparslan Sultan.

13
00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:57.759
Why did your grandfather
Ertugrul come to the borders?

14
00:03:57.880 --> 00:04:03.079
To walk on your path and turn those lands
into a homeland. my Haci Ahmed Sheikh.

15
00:04:03.600 --> 00:04:06.439
You made it a homcland
but could you follow the laws?

16
00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:09.279
A long as the blu sky
above does not collapse..

17
00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:11.719
And the dark ground
below does not split...

18
00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:17.399
who can take our homeland or
the laws we carved into our hearts?

19
00:04:17.520 --> 00:04:19.919
Who strays from the
laws loses his path.

20
00:04:20.080 --> 00:04:23.199
And he who loses the path
will have his land plundered.

21
00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:26.119
The life of such a man
will be taken by me first.

22
00:04:26.200 --> 00:04:30.159
But the Turks have lost their state
for the first time in a thousand years.

23
00:04:30.440 --> 00:04:35.999
The last Turkish state I built with great effort.
the Seljuks. were torn apart and destroyed.

24
00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:38.799
Are you not afraid of the
burden on your shoulders?

25
00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:45.159
If I have a bit of fear. let my bloodline perish.
let my flesh be torn apart and burned as wood in hell.

26
00:04:45.760 --> 00:04:49.279
Did your father sacrifice
you for this path?

27
00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:52.079
He did.

28
00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:55.279
Then how will you
walk on this road

29
00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:57.519
Will you stand
against your father?

30
00:04:57.640 --> 00:04:59.799
Will you crush your brother?

31
00:05:00.040 --> 00:05:02.639
Will you draw your
sword against your Beys?

32
00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:05.359
Answer me. Will you
kill your own father?

33
00:05:05.400 --> 00:05:09.599
Will you stain your hands with the
blood of your brothers and your Beys?

34
00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:13.119
Whoever follows the laws.
gains kut (the authority to rule)...

35
00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:17.279
whoever does not follow it
will face the consequences.

36
00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:19.279
One cannot hurt his father...

37
00:05:19.640 --> 00:05:22.279
and there cannot be
a fight among brothers.

38
00:05:23.800 --> 00:05:28.119
And Beys won't be the companion
of someone who is not given the kut.

39
00:05:28.840 --> 00:05:33.439
But I know that two swords
cannot stay in one sheath.

40
00:05:33.520 --> 00:05:36.239
How could you survive
this trouble then?

41
00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:40.039
How? Without rising
up. how could you?

42
00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:45.079
Without having blood on your
hands. how could you? How? How?

43
00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:05.119
May it be good. my Allah.

44
00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:03.159
My Allah..

45
00:07:03.480 --> 00:07:07.599
You have lit up the darkness of the
night by showing me my ancestors.

46
00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:12.039
You have weighed my heart with
the words of those mubarak people.

47
00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:18.199
If this path is mine
let me stand tall.

48
00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:20.199
Open my way.

49
00:07:21.400 --> 00:07:29.359
If I am going to be tested with my father and my
brother. fill my heart not with grudge. but with mercy.

50
00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:38.799
Let me draw the sword that I will take in my hand
to protect the laws. against my own nafs. my Allah.

51
00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:41.519
If my heart is going
to be tested with fire...

52
00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:44.239
Test my heart...

53
00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:48.679
But let that fire
help me grow...

54
00:07:48.880 --> 00:07:52.119
Do not burn me with it.

55
00:07:53.160 --> 00:07:55.799
Aameen.

56
00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:21.479
The Beys are really strong. Balaban!
They are too old Kara Halil!

57
00:08:21.560 --> 00:08:25.479
-They will get tired soon!
-Come on Balaban!

58
00:08:27.400 --> 00:08:30.319
-Come on Turhan!
-Come on brother!

59
00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:33.679
Come on Kara Halil!

60
00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:39.959
You shouldn't have
talked that much. Balaban

61
00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:44.719
This is the result of boasting. Alps.
Balaban. come on. get up!

62
00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:46.919
You cannot rest
right now. Come on!

63
00:08:46.920 --> 00:08:49.159
-Come on. get up! -Get up!

64
00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:55.639
Come on Kara Halil!

65
00:09:09.080 --> 00:09:11.119
I won!

66
00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:19.279
-I won!
-I think I crossed the line first.

67
00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:21.559
No you didn't! Are you blind?

68
00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.679
Ask Cerkutay Bey!

69
00:09:23.840 --> 00:09:25.599
No. not Cerkutay Bey.

70
00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:28.439
Cerkutay Bey is Osman
Bey's Bey. I cannot ask him.

71
00:09:28.520 --> 00:09:30.719
Shame on you. Kara Halil.

72
00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:33.999
Have you ever
seen me tell a he?

73
00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:37.239
Brother. wait.. Then
let s ask Beyzades.

74
00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:41.919
Tell me. Beyzades.

75
00:09:42.080 --> 00:09:44.359
Who is the winner
of this competition?

76
00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:46.479
Osman Bey s Beys...

77
00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:48.639
or Orhan Bey's Alps?

78
00:09:48.920 --> 00:09:51.679
-They both won.
-They crossed the line at the same time.

79
00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:53.799
Hay MashaAllah.

80
00:09:53.960 --> 00:09:56.439
If Turhan Bey hadn't
cheated. we would have won!

81
00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:58.679
Balaban!

82
00:10:00.160 --> 00:10:03.759
-Come on. Beyzades. Let's go...
-When you fell..

83
00:10:03.880 --> 00:10:06.439
You must ve hit your head.

84
00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:10.519
We are old men. son.

85
00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:15.319
-Cut this one! I'll eat this one.
-Kara Hahl!

86
00:10:16.360 --> 00:10:18.279
Kanturah sent this.

87
00:10:18.360 --> 00:10:19.679
Thank you.

88
00:10:20.440 --> 00:10:22.279
What is that lunatic saying?

89
00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:23.999
I'll see.

90
00:10:27.520 --> 00:10:30.479
It is not good.

91
00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:33.959
We need to inform our Orhan Bey.

92
00:10:34.560 --> 00:10:36.999
Come on Beys!

93
00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:53.799
How could you survive
this trouble then?

94
00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:57.159
How? Without rising
up. how could you?

95
00:10:57.560 --> 00:11:01.999
Without having blood on your
hands. how could you? How? How"?

96
00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:12.679
See boy?

97
00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:15.319
You were wondering
where Orhan Bey was.

98
00:11:15.560 --> 00:11:18.479
I told you we
would find him here.

99
00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:22.639
Perhaps. I was waiting for my
moon-faced timid bird to find me.

100
00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:24.959
Timid bird?

101
00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:29.039
Let's fly away then and see if
Orhan Bey can catch up with us.

102
00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:31.279
Come on come on!

103
00:11:34.280 --> 00:11:37.279
You're challenging
me? Here we go.

104
00:11:37.520 --> 00:11:40.039
Come on!

105
00:12:17.160 --> 00:12:19.799
What is the matter?

106
00:12:22.040 --> 00:12:25.199
Two swords cannot
fit into one sheath.

107
00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:28.439
However. drawing the other
sword out of the sheath...

108
00:12:28.680 --> 00:12:31.839
means being tested
with my brother and father.

109
00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:36.959
Only you can carry the
burden of this dream. Orhan.

110
00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:41.239
I and all your fellows and alps
believing in you will support you.

111
00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:44.399
When it's time.
so will Alaeddin.

112
00:12:45.200 --> 00:12:48.039
You are never on your own.

113
00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:11.439
We got news from Kanturali.

114
00:13:11.720 --> 00:13:13.679
It's not good. though.

115
00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:15.759
What is it?

116
00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:19.439
Seven thousands of Karesi.
Germiyan and Karaman soldiers.

117
00:13:20.400 --> 00:13:22.439
Their best commander
leading them.

118
00:13:22.520 --> 00:13:23.999
They are provoking us. my Bey.

119
00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:25.479
Seven thousands.

120
00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:29.919
With so many men. they can easily
enter our tribe and even Constantinople.

121
00:13:30.080 --> 00:13:31.559
How is that possible?

122
00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:34.559
What kind of Muslims. what
kind of relatives are they?

123
00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:39.919
My father is in the hot spring.

124
00:13:40.600 --> 00:13:43.439
Alaeddin is busy dealing
with the state business.

125
00:13:44.360 --> 00:13:47.279
It's our duty to stop that army.

126
00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:52.919
What are you talking about. Orhan? They
are seven thousands and you are only three.

127
00:13:53.160 --> 00:13:56.319
It's Ilkhanat that
Is feeding them.

128
00:13:56.680 --> 00:13:58.639
I will talk to Temurtas.

129
00:13:58.880 --> 00:14:00.519
I will handle this.

130
00:14:00.800 --> 00:14:04.439
You go to our tribe and
inform Alaeddin. Go ahead.

131
00:14:09.800 --> 00:14:13.839
My Bey. if there is a war. there will
be only one winner. which is Bursa.

132
00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:17.279
After the men we lose there.
Bursa will be only a dream for us.

133
00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:20.799
I won t let them turn my
father's dream into a nightmare.

134
00:14:21.120 --> 00:14:22.439
We will handle.

135
00:14:22.640 --> 00:14:24.079
Let's go.

136
00:14:24.320 --> 00:14:26.279
Come on.

137
00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:47.279
For every noker
of mine you killed.

138
00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:51.759
I will hang ten alps of
yours on the walls of Yarhisar.

139
00:14:52.160 --> 00:14:56.639
The great governor of Ilkhanate is
crying out for war and vowing vengeance.

140
00:14:57.000 --> 00:15:01.439
Temurtas. a picture
of courage and bravery!

141
00:15:15.560 --> 00:15:19.439
Would you like to
taste my fury. Flavius?

142
00:15:29.760 --> 00:15:32.879
I won t get my hands dirty
for the impertinent Kay|.

143
00:15:33.160 --> 00:15:36.039
You will do the job.

144
00:15:38.720 --> 00:15:42.239
The moment
Sahinshah attacks Bursa.

145
00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:47.519
Turkmen who I got equipped will march
through Yarhisar and attack their tribe.

146
00:15:48.160 --> 00:15:53.119
And from Yarhisar. I will watch the
rising flames in the tribe with pleasure.

147
00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:59.839
I will stick my dagger
into the heart of Kayi.

148
00:16:00.680 --> 00:16:05.239
Into the first land which
Ertugrul took from us. Sogut.

149
00:16:22.800 --> 00:16:24.839
Hasn't he spoken
yet. Aykurt Cavus?

150
00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:28.439
Not yet. but alps
are watching them.

151
00:16:28.760 --> 00:16:31.039
You should have told
us last night. Halime.

152
00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.239
Orhan's gone.

153
00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:35.839
I kept silent not to
spoil my brother's joy.

154
00:16:36.760 --> 00:16:39.279
He left so untimely.

155
00:16:39.680 --> 00:16:41.239
I know how to make him speak.

156
00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:44.639
We'll see how connected he is
to those who poisoned my father.

157
00:16:52.840 --> 00:16:55.199
You re making a
mistake. Bey's daughter.

158
00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:59.479
I have nothing to do with
what happened to Osman Bey.

159
00:17:01.440 --> 00:17:03.599
Speak.

160
00:17:03.920 --> 00:17:06.759
-I'm not a spy.
-Tell me then.

161
00:17:07.120 --> 00:17:10.719
What were you doing
in Orhan Bey's tent?

162
00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:18.359
Note.

163
00:17:25.600 --> 00:17:29.039
What is it? Speak!

164
00:17:30.520 --> 00:17:34.439
Speak if you don't want to die.

165
00:17:37.800 --> 00:17:40.559
I know how to
unseal your tongue.

166
00:17:40.920 --> 00:17:42.599
Speak.

167
00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:44.599
I was going to put it
In Orhan Bey's tent.

168
00:17:44.720 --> 00:17:46.719
How do you know
what's written here?

169
00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:50.239
Why doing things secretly?
Why didn't you tell us??

170
00:17:50.800 --> 00:17:53.959
This is why you came
across us that day. right?

171
00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:57.839
It was just a trick to
enter the tribe. right?

172
00:17:58.200 --> 00:17:59.919
Aykurt Bey.

173
00:18:00.400 --> 00:18:04.279
If you give me some bread and
water. my tongue may be unsealed.

174
00:18:04.520 --> 00:18:06.999
Don't leave me to this mad girl!

175
00:18:07.360 --> 00:18:10.879
You call me mad girl?

176
00:18:14.760 --> 00:18:17.999
Fill your stomach with hay now!

177
00:18:21.880 --> 00:18:24.239
Orhan Bey showed up once...

178
00:18:24.560 --> 00:18:27.519
and then he
disappeared again.

179
00:18:28.680 --> 00:18:32.359
He left at dawn with his alps.

180
00:18:37.800 --> 00:18:40.919
I knew h was
leaving. Sahinshah Bey.

181
00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:42.799
He informed you.

182
00:18:43.080 --> 00:18:45.359
Did he take permission from you?

183
00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:50.639
Orhan Bey got informed that Turkmen Beys
would attack with seven thousands soldiers.

184
00:18:50.920 --> 00:18:53.079
He's trying to find
a way to stop them.

185
00:18:53.200 --> 00:18:55.479
The way to stop them is obvious.

186
00:18:55.760 --> 00:18:58.239
We'll send all our
troops to Bursa.

187
00:18:58.360 --> 00:19:01.279
As soon as we capture
Bursa. EvelAllah.

188
00:19:01.480 --> 00:19:03.719
we will march to them
with the whole army.

189
00:19:03.920 --> 00:19:06.239
With the joy of the
conquest of Bursa.

190
00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:12.759
we will bring both Germiyan and Karaman to
their knees under the command of Sahinshah Bey.

191
00:19:12.920 --> 00:19:17.959
I expected you to say such encouraging things
while Orhan Bey was commanding. Avci Bey.

192
00:19:18.120 --> 00:19:23.199
Beys. stop mentioning my
brother's name all the time.

193
00:19:24.680 --> 00:19:28.559
-Do I have permission?
-Come in. hatuns.

194
00:19:31.440 --> 00:19:33.959
You wanted to see me. my Bey?

195
00:19:35.640 --> 00:19:37.559
Listen. hatuns.

196
00:19:37.720 --> 00:19:40.959
The conquest of Bursa
means fighting in all fronts.

197
00:19:41.160 --> 00:19:44.839
Sisters will fight
in the front line too.

198
00:19:45.360 --> 00:19:49.239
Sahinshah Bey will send all
the troops to Bursa to capture it.

199
00:19:49.440 --> 00:19:54.919
For this reason. we should reinforce the
defense of the other fronts and our tribe.

200
00:19:56.800 --> 00:19:58.879
I'm tired of
waiting in the tribe.

201
00:19:59.040 --> 00:20:04.439
If you let me. I want to go to the
army camp with my loyal Beys.

202
00:20:05.080 --> 00:20:07.639
You have my permission.
Sahinshah Bey.

203
00:20:17.160 --> 00:20:18.999
-Fatma.
-Yes. my Bey?

204
00:20:19.120 --> 00:20:22.759
With the team of Sisters. you
will support the alps in Sogut.

205
00:20:22.760 --> 00:20:24.119
Start your preparations.

206
00:20:24.120 --> 00:20:29.439
Halime will stay here in the tribe with
one group of Sisters to defend the tribe.

207
00:20:29.960 --> 00:20:31.639
Gonca. Nilufer. Didar Hatun.

208
00:20:31.680 --> 00:20:33.599
You're in charge
of manufacturing.

209
00:20:33.720 --> 00:20:36.719
You should get everybody
armed as soon as possible.

210
00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:40.639
May Allah help and bless us.

211
00:20:40.840 --> 00:20:43.039
-Aameen.
-Aameen

212
00:20:58.760 --> 00:21:00.359
Don't cook the meat.

213
00:21:00.440 --> 00:21:02.359
Don't cook! Enough.

214
00:21:02.520 --> 00:21:06.399
Raw! The rawer. the better!

215
00:21:06.800 --> 00:21:11.039
The meat must have
blood on it Flavius.

216
00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:27.519
You once cooked a
commander who lost the battle.

217
00:21:28.680 --> 00:21:30.599
They say so.

218
00:21:31.280 --> 00:21:33.479
Is it true;

219
00:21:37.600 --> 00:21:39.759
No.

220
00:21:40.160 --> 00:21:42.399
I ate him raw too.

221
00:21:49.520 --> 00:21:52.279
But I like being
known like that.

222
00:21:52.640 --> 00:21:57.399
People will obey you according
to how they know you. Flavius

223
00:21:57.800 --> 00:22:03.079
Tell this story in Sogut too. So they will
shake with fear when they even hear my name.

224
00:22:40.600 --> 00:22:43.359
Orhan wants to talk.

225
00:22:45.560 --> 00:22:48.279
With peace and silence.

226
00:22:51.080 --> 00:22:55.199
He's risking his life. which means
he's come all the way for a good reason.

227
00:22:55.360 --> 00:22:57.279
Orhan!

228
00:22:57.880 --> 00:23:00.159
Join our table!

229
00:23:00.600 --> 00:23:03.279
If you want to talk.

230
00:23:03.520 --> 00:23:06.359
we should talk
before you die.

231
00:23:23.800 --> 00:23:26.679
Selamun aleykum. Temurtas.

232
00:23:30.080 --> 00:23:34.679
Whoever has a death
wish runs to the executioner.

233
00:23:36.760 --> 00:23:39.719
Aleykum selam.

234
00:23:48.680 --> 00:23:50.999
How is your father doing?

235
00:23:52.520 --> 00:23:53.719
Is he fine?

236
00:23:53.880 --> 00:23:56.839
He's fine. thanks to Allah.

237
00:23:57.200 --> 00:23:58.879
Alaeddin...

238
00:23:59.480 --> 00:24:02.759
proved his healing skills.

239
00:24:09.120 --> 00:24:10.999
Well. Orhan...

240
00:24:11.160 --> 00:24:13.199
Speak.

241
00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:16.599
I'm listening in silence.

242
00:24:18.400 --> 00:24:21.399
We shouldn't do that in haste.

243
00:24:21.760 --> 00:24:26.079
I sent a message to the commanders of
Karesi. Germiyan and Karaman Beylics.

244
00:24:26.640 --> 00:24:27.999
They must be on their way.

245
00:24:28.000 --> 00:24:32.199
When they come.
we will eat and chat.

246
00:24:33.400 --> 00:24:36.359
Make the meat well-cooked.

247
00:24:50.120 --> 00:24:51.999
Deliver this immediately.

248
00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:54.399
As you order. my Bey.

249
00:24:58.000 --> 00:25:01.279
-Hatun.
-My Alaeddin.

250
00:25:01.880 --> 00:25:04.879
Alaeddin Bey I know
you re out of time. but...

251
00:25:05.120 --> 00:25:08.199
I will introduce
Colpan to you.

252
00:25:08.520 --> 00:25:10.239
Estaghfirullah. Go ahead.

253
00:25:10.280 --> 00:25:14.279
My Bey. I'm Colpan. daughter of Avci
Bey one of your loyalest Beys Avci Bey.

254
00:25:14.280 --> 00:25:15.759
Is that so?

255
00:25:16.040 --> 00:25:18.839
Colpan is very good at archery.

256
00:25:19.000 --> 00:25:21.239
She never misses
her target. my Bey.

257
00:25:24.680 --> 00:25:30.159
With your permission. I want to join Halime
Hatun's Sisters as an archer. my Bey.

258
00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:36.359
We are at war. We need
everyone who can use a weapon.

259
00:25:36.440 --> 00:25:38.839
Welcome. sister.

260
00:25:55.560 --> 00:25:59.679
Karesi. Germiyan. Karaman.

261
00:26:00.120 --> 00:26:03.679
So many people are
willing to overthrow Kayi.

262
00:26:05.200 --> 00:26:08.999
See how enthusiastic they
are to fight against you?

263
00:26:09.400 --> 00:26:11.879
Ilkhanate never fight.

264
00:26:12.120 --> 00:26:15.279
We storm around
and burn things down.

265
00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:21.079
Come by our tribe sometime. We can
prepare such good tables for you too.

266
00:26:22.320 --> 00:26:27.159
We can also talk about the torture
you performed against Oghuzs.

267
00:26:27.280 --> 00:26:31.079
Stop disgracing my table with empty
talk. Just say what you need to say.

268
00:26:31.240 --> 00:26:33.679
And then die.

269
00:26:39.200 --> 00:26:44.799
Do you think my brother. who dared to fight all of
you in the conquest of Bursa didn't take measures?

270
00:26:47.000 --> 00:26:49.719
Don't be so naive.

271
00:26:51.160 --> 00:26:52.599
The fire burning here...

272
00:26:52.680 --> 00:26:56.199
Is the condition of your tribe
when you attack Bursa. Orhan.

273
00:26:56.280 --> 00:26:57.519
Look at it carefully.

274
00:26:57.640 --> 00:27:01.079
You will all burn in
those flames. Flavius.

275
00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:10.199
And you will regret not accepting
Orhan's offer when the day comes.

276
00:27:12.480 --> 00:27:16.639
None of your offers can stop us.

277
00:27:17.720 --> 00:27:23.839
I won't stop you. I will stop
my brother and Sahinshah Bey.

278
00:27:25.160 --> 00:27:27.839
I will end the siege.

279
00:27:49.360 --> 00:27:51.159
Halime!

280
00:27:51.400 --> 00:27:52.799
Come here!

281
00:27:52.920 --> 00:27:55.839
-What happened Iraz Hatun?
-Just come here!

282
00:27:56.960 --> 00:27:58.639
Come here.

283
00:27:59.000 --> 00:28:03.279
-What happened?
-Give those arrows to me.

284
00:28:04.280 --> 00:28:06.679
Move.

285
00:28:07.440 --> 00:28:09.839
Hold this. Hold it.

286
00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:13.559
What am I going to do with this Iraz
Hatun? I am here to protect the Hatuns!

287
00:28:13.560 --> 00:28:16.159
You will prote t them and wash
the clothes at the same time.

288
00:28:16.200 --> 00:28:17.399
Malhun Hatun said that...

289
00:28:17.440 --> 00:28:20.879
So that you are not giving up on your
sword. you will do both at the same time.

290
00:28:20.920 --> 00:28:22.279
Move Move.

291
00:28:22.320 --> 00:28:23.719
Am I going to wash them?

292
00:28:23.760 --> 00:28:26.479
You are. Come on!

293
00:28:28.920 --> 00:28:30.199
Watch me do it.

294
00:28:30.760 --> 00:28:33.159
You will do it like
this. Come on!

295
00:28:33.200 --> 00:28:35.999
Come on! Let us see the
strength of your arms! Come on!

296
00:28:36.120 --> 00:28:39.199
-Hit it! Harder! -Ah mother...

297
00:28:39.400 --> 00:28:41.919
Mother. what am
I even doing here?

298
00:28:42.960 --> 00:28:44.519
Give that to me Look!

299
00:28:44.720 --> 00:28:48.719
Hit as if you are hitting the
ilnfidels! Hit as if you are training!

300
00:28:50.360 --> 00:28:54.119
Mother. Ah mother! I should
be with my brothers right now.

301
00:28:54.360 --> 00:28:56.559
Right... Hit harder.

302
00:28:56.760 --> 00:28:59.479
Hit it

303
00:28:59.560 --> 00:29:01.999
Eyes down! Come on!

304
00:29:02.560 --> 00:29:05.239
Well done.

305
00:29:06.000 --> 00:29:07.599
Stop complaining! Come on!

306
00:29:08.480 --> 00:29:10.439
Turn it around.

307
00:29:10.720 --> 00:29:13.399
-May it be easy. sisters.
-Thank you.

308
00:29:13.760 --> 00:29:15.679
Welcome Fatma Hatun.

309
00:29:15.840 --> 00:29:17.199
Sister...

310
00:29:17.280 --> 00:29:19.879
I came here to ask for my
Halime sister's pardon but...

311
00:29:20.200 --> 00:29:22.079
Sister. save me from this place.

312
00:29:22.240 --> 00:29:24.559
No... I promised Malhun Hatun.

313
00:29:24.560 --> 00:29:27.799
You will not go anywhere before
you learn how to wash clothes!

314
00:29:27.800 --> 00:29:30.959
Come on. Come
with me. Fatma Hatun.

315
00:29:34.200 --> 00:29:35.559
Sister...

316
00:29:35.640 --> 00:29:39.159
Where did my mother's desire to
teach you this come from? Tell me.

317
00:29:39.960 --> 00:29:41.359
Of course you don't know.

318
00:29:41.520 --> 00:29:44.479
Malhun mother will marry
us with Beys who she sees fit.

319
00:29:44.560 --> 00:29:46.599
She is serious this time.

320
00:29:46.720 --> 00:29:48.519
What?

321
00:29:49.200 --> 00:29:51.479
Did my mother say that?

322
00:30:00.960 --> 00:30:04.359
Have you heard it?
Orhan will lift the siege.

323
00:30:04.880 --> 00:30:07.039
Not only that...

324
00:30:08.000 --> 00:30:13.999
I will let Ilkhanids
and Turk Beylics trade.

325
00:30:18.520 --> 00:30:25.399
I will open the trade routes of
Bursa. Iznik. Izmit. and Constantinople.

326
00:30:27.800 --> 00:30:35.079
I will even personally ensure the safety of
your caravans passing through our lands.

327
00:30:39.040 --> 00:30:41.199
I wonder if the
meat poisoned you.

328
00:30:41.400 --> 00:30:44.039
Has the air here affected
you badly. Orhan?

329
00:30:44.480 --> 00:30:48.839
-What you want is what we all want.
-But...

330
00:30:49.960 --> 00:30:52.599
Those who trade will
pay taxes to me first.

331
00:30:52.920 --> 00:30:56.359
Your share will stay the
same Temurtas. Don't worry.

332
00:30:58.200 --> 00:31:00.839
Do you believe
what you just said?

333
00:31:01.040 --> 00:31:06.199
If the reason for your alliance
Is to end the siege of Bursa...

334
00:31:06.520 --> 00:31:10.239
then I am the only one
who can end it without a battle.

335
00:31:14.360 --> 00:31:16.439
Who are you?

336
00:31:16.640 --> 00:31:17.359
Who?

337
00:31:18.640 --> 00:31:21.439
Your father has taken
away your authority.

338
00:31:21.560 --> 00:31:24.919
You are just an ordinary Bey.
Why would they listen to you?

339
00:31:24.960 --> 00:31:27.199
If not with words. I
will do it with swords.

340
00:31:27.480 --> 00:31:30.279
If they stand against me. I
will make them bow by force.

341
00:31:32.000 --> 00:31:39.959
If necessary. I will bring peace by fighting
together with my Alps and Beys loyal to me.

342
00:31:42.000 --> 00:31:44.399
What about your father?

343
00:31:44.760 --> 00:31:47.559
If necessary. I will
face him as well.

344
00:31:47.840 --> 00:31:50.799
I won't hesitate.

345
00:31:56.880 --> 00:31:59.519
I should go.

346
00:32:00.680 --> 00:32:05.079
The meat looks good. It will
taste really delicious with thyme.

347
00:32:05.800 --> 00:32:10.359
I will go. take over the
headquarters. and end the siege.

348
00:32:10.520 --> 00:32:13.959
Either you will take
my head. or Sahinshah.

349
00:32:14.080 --> 00:32:16.599
Orhan...

350
00:32:17.200 --> 00:32:18.839
Go now.

351
00:32:18.880 --> 00:32:21.359
But if you falil...

352
00:32:21.560 --> 00:32:26.319
Tomorrow I will come at you with
an even greater furor. know that.

353
00:32:28.680 --> 00:32:31.359
Selamun aleykum.

354
00:32:33.000 --> 00:32:34.519
Ve aleykum selam.

355
00:32:49.040 --> 00:32:51.399
Do you trust him?

356
00:32:56.800 --> 00:32:58.439
We'll see.

357
00:32:58.880 --> 00:33:00.799
Tomorrow.

358
00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:08.359
You got out of there alive
thanks to Allah. my Bey.

359
00:33:08.520 --> 00:33:09.719
Sure I did.

360
00:33:09.920 --> 00:33:12.879
I offered them what they
wanted on a golden platter.

361
00:33:13.240 --> 00:33:15.559
Did they accept your offer?

362
00:33:15.600 --> 00:33:19.719
We ve gained one
day. Just one single day.

363
00:33:20.040 --> 00:33:23.919
We will capture Bursa that day
without a single Alp getting injured.

364
00:33:24.120 --> 00:33:25.919
Then it will be Temurtas' turn.

365
00:33:25.960 --> 00:33:29.479
I will show him the result of
attempting to take my father's life.

366
00:33:29.760 --> 00:33:32.279
But we need time. Let's go.

367
00:33:32.520 --> 00:33:34.519
We have to stop that war.

368
00:33:34.600 --> 00:33:36.519
Come on.

369
00:33:45.520 --> 00:33:50.479
Orhan knows that you were
the one who poisoned Osman.

370
00:33:51.120 --> 00:33:53.119
And I also do.

371
00:33:56.120 --> 00:33:58.639
But he isn't saying it
so openly to my face.

372
00:33:59.280 --> 00:34:02.079
Flavius.

373
00:34:04.840 --> 00:34:09.719
He understands politics as
much as he understands war.

374
00:34:13.240 --> 00:34:17.719
A voice inside me says
he will do what he said.

375
00:34:22.920 --> 00:34:24.439
We'll see.

376
00:34:24.600 --> 00:34:27.399
You wait for word from me.

377
00:34:27.960 --> 00:34:33.199
We will wait one more day
to handle this without war.

378
00:34:41.280 --> 00:34:44.479
Not only us. she will also
marry my Alaeddin brother.

379
00:34:44.520 --> 00:34:46.999
But Alaeddin brother
will not accept it.

380
00:34:47.200 --> 00:34:50.119
If we unite. we can
oppose to her. sister.

381
00:34:50.200 --> 00:34:53.479
I told my mother! I won't get
married with someone I don't love!

382
00:34:56.040 --> 00:34:59.239
My father? Does
my father know this?

383
00:34:59.400 --> 00:35:01.439
He apparently does.

384
00:35:02.320 --> 00:35:06.839
But I am determined. I
will not get married. sister!

385
00:35:13.040 --> 00:35:16.119
Don't be childish. Halime.
We are the Bey's daughters.

386
00:35:16.160 --> 00:35:19.439
We will marry whoever my
mother and father deem suitable.

387
00:35:19.640 --> 00:35:21.119
Sure. little Malhun Hatun.

388
00:35:21.240 --> 00:35:23.959
-Halime.. -What?

389
00:35:25.000 --> 00:35:27.119
Look. Iraz Hatun
never got married.

390
00:35:27.160 --> 00:35:29.359
So not veryone has
to get married. sister!

391
00:35:29.360 --> 00:35:30.359
No.

392
00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:33.119
I got married three times!

393
00:35:34.160 --> 00:35:37.559
-What do you mean?
-They all died.

394
00:35:40.600 --> 00:35:44.079
But wait.. I will get married
once I find the forth one.

395
00:35:44.080 --> 00:35:45.679
I am waiting for the right man.

396
00:35:45.760 --> 00:35:47.439
Loneliness is difficult.

397
00:35:47.640 --> 00:35:50.039
By the way Malhun
Hatun is right.

398
00:35:50.160 --> 00:35:54.159
It is time for you to marry.
You need to get married!

399
00:35:59.400 --> 00:36:02.919
What do you have in your hand.
sister? You keep looking at it.

400
00:36:07.480 --> 00:36:10.959
Come on. Come on.

401
00:36:14.400 --> 00:36:17.359
I am going to Sogut.
May it be easy to you.

402
00:36:17.360 --> 00:36:19.239
Sister. save me
from this place...

403
00:36:19.320 --> 00:36:21.999
You'll do 1t. come on!

404
00:36:24.800 --> 00:36:28.239
Come on sisters! May it be easy!
Thank you. Fatma Hatun

405
00:36:28.440 --> 00:36:31.639
Come on! Move!

406
00:36:33.920 --> 00:36:37.679
Don't look at me Why are you
looking at me? Mind your business! Go!

407
00:36:38.200 --> 00:36:40.759
Ah mother. ah!

408
00:37:04.720 --> 00:37:08.999
-Selamun aleykum.
-Aleykum selam.

409
00:37:09.320 --> 00:37:10.839
Welcome. my Bey.

410
00:37:11.040 --> 00:37:13.559
You returned safely.
thanks to Allah.

411
00:37:13.640 --> 00:37:16.599
Have I ever come here any
other way. my Cerkutay Bey?

412
00:37:16.720 --> 00:37:19.079
Why did you get worried?

413
00:37:19.880 --> 00:37:21.559
You went to Temurtas.

414
00:37:21.760 --> 00:37:24.079
After killing all his soldiers.

415
00:37:24.320 --> 00:37:29.119
The anger of the
Mongols is legendary.

416
00:37:30.320 --> 00:37:34.119
I'm telling this
because I know that...

417
00:37:34.480 --> 00:37:36.239
I told Cerkutay that...

418
00:37:36.480 --> 00:37:38.279
we should come after you.

419
00:37:38.360 --> 00:37:41.959
Osman Bey entrusted his
children to us in his absence.

420
00:37:42.080 --> 00:37:45.319
And I told Boran Bey that
Orhan Bey would protect himself...

421
00:37:45.600 --> 00:37:49.519
But there would be no one to
protect the tribe. So I said no.

422
00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:52.279
Is this your duty. Beys?

423
00:37:52.440 --> 00:37:54.999
Where are the Alps>

424
00:37:59.120 --> 00:38:00.719
Alaeddin Bey ...

425
00:38:00.880 --> 00:38:04.999
sent all the Alps to the headquarters.
to Sahinshah Bey. my Orhan.

426
00:38:23.960 --> 00:38:26.719
Alaeddin.

427
00:38:26.880 --> 00:38:28.639
Brother...

428
00:38:28.680 --> 00:38:30.079
What is the situation?

429
00:38:30.320 --> 00:38:32.039
You sent our Alps to Bursa.

430
00:38:32.080 --> 00:38:35.839
The longer the conquest is delayed.
the more the enemy is encouraged.

431
00:38:35.880 --> 00:38:38.439
The Beys are worried. brother.

432
00:38:39.000 --> 00:38:40.599
Gather the council. Alaeddin.

433
00:38:40.720 --> 00:38:43.479
We just had a council!
Gather it again. Alaeddin!

434
00:38:43.560 --> 00:38:45.359
Brother. what are
you trying to say?

435
00:38:45.360 --> 00:38:47.079
I sent all the troops to Bursa.

436
00:38:47.120 --> 00:38:49.399
All the Beys and
Commanders are in Bursa.

437
00:38:49.440 --> 00:38:52.039
Bursa will be ours once
the sun rises. InshaAllah.

438
00:38:52.120 --> 00:38:54.319
Not today. Alaeddin!

439
00:38:54.440 --> 00:38:56.279
You will lift the siege!

440
00:38:56.440 --> 00:38:59.879
Bursa will wait for
us a little longer!

441
00:39:01.720 --> 00:39:03.119
It won't. brother!

442
00:39:03.240 --> 00:39:06.319
Alaeddin... You are
making a mistake. Alaeddin!

443
00:39:06.600 --> 00:39:08.799
I said the siege
won t be lifted. brother!

444
00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:11.039
I sent everyone to Bursa!
What are you even saying?!

445
00:39:11.080 --> 00:39:12.599
You will lift the
siege. Alaeddin!

446
00:39:12.640 --> 00:39:14.159
Kayi s future depends on this!

447
00:39:14.160 --> 00:39:16.719
My Allah... Let this end well.

448
00:39:17.280 --> 00:39:18.479
What 1s happening here?

449
00:39:18.600 --> 00:39:20.559
There 1s a storm
inside. Malhun Hatun.

450
00:39:20.560 --> 00:39:24.039
If you care about Kayi's future.
then you know we have to take Bursa!

451
00:39:24.040 --> 00:39:26.199
You will withdraw
that army today!

452
00:39:26.320 --> 00:39:28.439
That's the end of discussion

453
00:39:30.120 --> 00:39:32.639
I gave the order!
Bursa will be taken!

454
00:39:32.640 --> 00:39:35.439
Our army i1s going to Bursa!
Tomorrow. all this will end!

455
00:39:35.520 --> 00:39:38.359
If we attack Bursa. they
will end you. Alaeddin.

456
00:39:38.360 --> 00:39:40.799
They will end our tribe.
the dream of our father.

457
00:39:42.600 --> 00:39:44.759
I am ordering you. Orhan Bey.

458
00:39:44.760 --> 00:39:46.279
You will go to Karacahisar.

459
00:39:46.320 --> 00:39:48.159
I will go to the headquarters.

460
00:39:48.240 --> 00:39:50.279
And I will end the
war once 1 go there

461
00:39:50.280 --> 00:39:52.879
Don't .. Don't you
dare. Orhan Bey!

462
00:39:52.880 --> 00:39:55.359
There is no turning back
from this path. Know that.

463
00:39:55.360 --> 00:39:57.839
Orhan! Alaeddin!
What are you doing?!

464
00:39:58.000 --> 00:40:00.759
If we attack Bursa. we
will lose our lands. mother!

465
00:40:00.800 --> 00:40:03.479
How are we going to
stop Temurtas' army?!

466
00:40:03.480 --> 00:40:06.319
-I went there. spoke to him. and we made an agreement.
-What?

467
00:40:06.360 --> 00:40:08.079
Did you make an
agreement with Temurtas?!

468
00:40:08.120 --> 00:40:09.719
Did you shake hands
with our enemy?

469
00:40:09.720 --> 00:40:12.599
Fortunately my father is not here
and he is not hearing your words!

470
00:40:12.600 --> 00:40:14.079
What happens if he hears me?

471
00:40:14.080 --> 00:40:15.919
Is he going to take
my command rank?

472
00:40:15.920 --> 00:40:17.279
Is he going to exile me?

473
00:40:17.320 --> 00:40:18.639
Orhan! Alaeddin!

474
00:40:18.760 --> 00:40:20.359
Make your decision. Alaeddin!

475
00:40:20.440 --> 00:40:25.079
Will you go to the headquarters and tell
them? Or should I go there and do it for you?

476
00:40:25.160 --> 00:40:29.319
You must crush me
first to leave Orhan Bey.

477
00:40:29.400 --> 00:40:31.799
Then I will crush you and leave.

478
00:40:33.680 --> 00:40:37.239
-Enough!
-My Bey!

479
00:40:37.400 --> 00:40:40.479
Stop! What are you doing?!

480
00:40:40.640 --> 00:40:44.439
Enough! Stop
What are you doing?!

481
00:40:51.560 --> 00:40:53.519
If we don't have the same path

482
00:40:53.680 --> 00:40:55.999
don't stand in my
path anymore. Alaeddin.

483
00:40:59.120 --> 00:41:01.999
Kara Halil. Balaban.

484
00:41:02.480 --> 00:41:03.959
Gather the alps.

485
00:41:04.080 --> 00:41:06.479
Boran Bey. Cerkutay Bey.

486
00:41:06.800 --> 00:41:08.879
Stop Orhan Bey.

487
