without my permission.

493
00:41:32.880 --> 00:41:36.359
-Alaeddin.
-I won't say it again.

494
00:41:37.400 --> 00:41:40.999
Otherwise. you will answer to
Osman Bey when he is back.

495
00:41:51.480 --> 00:41:53.559
Alps.

496
00:41:54.480 --> 00:41:57.279
This is Alaeddin Bey's order.

497
