back side of this inn.

525
00:45:54.240 --> 00:45:58.999
Fatma Hatun. welcome.
Welcome. Fatma Hatun.

526
00:46:06.720 --> 00:46:09.519
-Selamun aleykum. -Aleykum selam.
-Fatma..

527
00:46:09.800 --> 00:46:12.639
Archers. take
positions on the roofs.

528
