730
01:12:28.080 --> 01:12:31.319
AbdurRahman!

731
01:12:42.200 --> 01:12:44.559
Kanturali!

732
01:13:57.160 --> 01:13:58.999
My Bey..

733
01:13:59.400 --> 01:14:01.519
Can we..

