down the last one wins.

738
01:15:00.880 --> 01:15:03.159
I think you are even

739
01:15:07.240 --> 01:15:09.319
What does our laws say?

740
01:15:09.480 --> 01:15:13.279
The Beys speak. but the
Hatuns have the last word.

741
01:15:13.600 --> 01:15:14.519
Right?

742
01:15:16.800 --> 01:15:19.879
My dear brother. come here!

743
01:15:32.400 --> 01:15:34.879
I missed fighting
side by side with you.

744
01:15:34.960 --> 01:15:37.519
It ended very quickly. my Bey.

745
01:15:40.640 --> 01:15:42.559
Oh no...

746
01:15:42.640 --> 01:15:46.319
Someone forgot dying
Remind him then.

747
01:15:55.520 --> 01:15:57.519
He won't forget again.

748
01:15:57.600 --> 01:16:01.679
Where have you
been all this time?

749
01:16:02.000 --> 01:16:07.839
I had sent AbdurRahman to Karaman
and Kanturali to Germiyan for observation.

750
01:16:08.240 --> 01:16:11.519
Our reason for coming here
is not just these dogs. my Bey.

751
01:16:11.680 --> 01:16:13.239
We have important news for you.

752
01:16:13.520 --> 01:16:16.239
You have the
actual news. my Bey.

753
01:16:16.440 --> 01:16:19.759
What are you doing here?
Why ar you here alone?

754
01:16:19.920 --> 01:16:22.479
How did they learn where
you were and find you?

755
01:16:22.640 --> 01:16:24.319
We will find out.

756
01:16:24.480 --> 01:16:26.079
We have a lot to talk about.

757
01:16:26.120 --> 01:16:27.279
We don't have much time.

758
01:16:27.280 --> 01:16:30.119
First. let's go and help our
brothers. then we will talk.

759
01:16:30.240 --> 01:16:31.879
Which brothers?

760
01:16:32.000 --> 01:16:34.319
You'll see when we go there.

761
01:16:34.960 --> 01:16:37.079
Come on.

762
01:16:48.040 --> 01:16:50.959
Welcome to Yarhisar
castle. Governor Temurtas.

763
01:16:51.240 --> 01:16:53.239
Come inside. Let us host you.

764
01:16:53.320 --> 01:16:55.479
Osman has made
this place prosperous.

765
01:16:55.800 --> 01:16:58.439
It can rival many
magnificent cities.

766
01:16:58.600 --> 01:17:00.439
It would suit me right?

767
01:17:00.440 --> 01:17:03.959
-Right. Governor Hadhrat.
-Why are you here?

768
01:17:08.480 --> 01:17:10.319
To water...

769
01:17:11.400 --> 01:17:15.559
our swords with your blood.

770
01:17:50.080 --> 01:17:54.039
Burn this place down!

771
01:17:55.080 --> 01:18:00.079
Kayi's stupid Beys will
remember the strength of Ilkhanate!

772
01:18:21.120 --> 01:18:24.359
What are we going to do with
these. Governor Temurtas?

773
01:18:48.840 --> 01:18:50.679
Kayi...

774
01:18:50.760 --> 01:18:54.159
forgot that peace with
Mongols is a blessing...

775
01:18:54.320 --> 01:18:58.599
and being in a war
with Mongols is a disaster.

776
01:19:06.160 --> 01:19:09.439
Send their dead
bodies to their tribe!

777
01:19:10.240 --> 01:19:11.839
They will remember again!

778
01:19:12.000 --> 01:19:15.079
As you order. my Governor.

779
01:19:23.960 --> 01:19:27.399
Hay MashaAllah. Hay MashaAllah.

780
01:19:27.440 --> 01:19:30.559
Such a thing has never been
seen In the history of the Kayi.

781
01:19:30.600 --> 01:19:34.839
Troops are pouring into our
headquarters from all four sides.

782
01:19:35.560 --> 01:19:37.799
MashaAllah.

783
01:19:49.080 --> 01:19:52.639
Orhan Bey's Alps have also come.

784
01:20:05.120 --> 01:20:06.839
May it be good Beys.

785
01:20:07.040 --> 01:20:10.519
Whoever looks at
your face gets worried.

786
01:20:11.480 --> 01:20:14.319
It's not good. Sahinshah Bey.

787
01:20:14.520 --> 01:20:18.399
Alaeddin Bey exiled
Orhan Bey to Karacahisar.

788
01:20:25.840 --> 01:20:29.959
Alaeddin Bey has removed the
obstacle in front of the conquest of Bursa.

789
01:20:30.120 --> 01:20:32.919
Is that why you
are worried. Beys;

790
01:20:34.920 --> 01:20:37.079
The finger cut by
justice does not hurt.

791
01:20:37.360 --> 01:20:40.079
Alaeddin Bey
did the right thing.

792
01:20:40.200 --> 01:20:43.839
And we will do our
duties. evelAllah.

793
01:20:43.960 --> 01:20:48.079
When someone says gaza. crazy horses
start running in our hearts. Sahinshah Bey.

794
01:20:48.240 --> 01:20:51.639
Bursa is the dream of Osman
Bey. the father of veterans.

795
01:20:51.720 --> 01:20:53.919
We will sacrifice
our lives for that city.

796
01:20:53.920 --> 01:20:57.839
What makes me think is the words of
Orhan Bey. InshaAllah he is not right.

797
01:20:58.000 --> 01:21:00.679
And Bursa won't bring disasters.

798
01:21:01.240 --> 01:21:05.959
Disaster is far from us and
close to the enemy. Turhan Bey.

799
01:21:06.280 --> 01:21:10.639
You will go and take the news of
conquest to Orhan Bey tomorrow.

800
01:21:11.080 --> 01:21:13.319
He will get happy as well.

801
01:21:17.920 --> 01:21:20.439
Alps!

802
01:21:23.200 --> 01:21:24.919
Tomorrow. Bursa..

803
01:21:25.040 --> 01:21:28.319
Will echo with the clash
of my warriors" swords.

804
01:21:28.480 --> 01:21:32.079
Long live Sahinshah Bey!
Long live Sahinshah Bey!

805
01:21:32.240 --> 01:21:34.719
Long live Sahinshah Bey!

806
01:21:34.800 --> 01:21:39.399
Osman Bey will be the
owner of the victory. not me.

807
01:21:39.880 --> 01:21:42.039
Bursa is his dream!

808
01:21:42.040 --> 01:21:47.839
Long live Osman Bey!
Long live Osman Bey!

809
01:21:48.040 --> 01:21:51.439
Tomorrow I will go
to my Osman Bey...

810
01:21:51.520 --> 01:21:55.599
Are you ready to go back to your home
tomorrow. to your Hatuns. your sisters...

811
01:21:55.760 --> 01:22:01.919
with bloody swords in your hand
that will help you conquer Bursa?!

812
01:22:01.920 --> 01:22:05.199
We are ready! We are ready!

813
01:22:05.240 --> 01:22:07.079
Victory is ours.

814
01:22:07.280 --> 01:22:11.839
But.. let's follow
the rules of war.

815
01:22:11.880 --> 01:22:13.879
Send word to Lord Saroz.

816
01:22:13.960 --> 01:22:18.039
Tell him Sahinshah Bey wants
to give him a last chance...

817
01:22:18.440 --> 01:22:22.479
before he destroys Bursa.

818
01:22:51.720 --> 01:22:54.279
Orhan Bey s coming.

819
01:22:59.120 --> 01:23:01.279
With his mad men.

820
01:23:01.560 --> 01:23:04.439
-Selamun aleykum.
-Aleykum selam.

821
01:23:04.960 --> 01:23:07.279
-Balaban.
-My Bey.

822
01:23:07.400 --> 01:23:08.879
Thanks to Allah.

823
01:23:09.160 --> 01:23:12.399
Now that I've seen
you. I can die in peace.

824
01:23:13.320 --> 01:23:17.119
The only place you would go in
peace Is the battlefield. Balaban.

825
01:23:19.880 --> 01:23:21.839
Not this time.

826
01:23:32.880 --> 01:23:35.079
Stop crying like
a baby. Balaban.

827
01:23:36.680 --> 01:23:39.119
It's already over.

828
01:23:41.960 --> 01:23:44.079
We call him bad for a reason.

829
01:23:44.360 --> 01:23:47.599
You're good. Stop
souring your face.

830
01:23:50.000 --> 01:23:54.639
Boran Bey. Cerkutay Bey.
Glorious Beys of Osman Bey.

831
01:23:57.320 --> 01:24:00.959
Abdurrahman. Kantural.

832
01:24:01.840 --> 01:24:04.119
Orhan Bey's mad alps.

833
01:24:04.560 --> 01:24:07.439
Weren t you in the land of
Germiyan and Karaman?

834
01:24:07.560 --> 01:24:10.919
Yes. we were. We heard the
sword sounds and we came.

835
01:24:17.920 --> 01:24:21.319
While are you grinning
like a goat seeing the hay?

836
01:24:21.600 --> 01:24:23.279
I hit the last one.

837
01:24:23.640 --> 01:24:25.439
No way!

838
01:24:26.000 --> 01:24:28.479
That man was
already on the ground.

839
01:24:30.520 --> 01:24:34.799
They never change. my Bey. They
are still fighting to overcome each other.

840
01:24:35.800 --> 01:24:40.679
Let's go. We need to
overcome something else now.

841
01:24:40.960 --> 01:24:44.399
-Find somewhere to stay for the night.
-Brother.

842
01:24:45.360 --> 01:24:49.759
Move. I aught this one
entering your tent secretly.

843
01:24:50.440 --> 01:24:53.439
He should answer to you.

844
01:25:01.680 --> 01:25:04.959
What were you doing in my tent?

845
01:25:08.840 --> 01:25:12.359
He said he would
leave this letter for you.

846
01:25:36.520 --> 01:25:39.039
Orhan Bey.

847
01:25:39.520 --> 01:25:45.719
Karesi and Germiyan are recruiting
armies with Temurtas orders.

848
01:25:47.120 --> 01:25:50.079
They will cooperate
with Saroz and Flavius.

849
01:25:50.240 --> 01:25:52.879
I want you to know this as
the glorious commander...

850
01:25:53.000 --> 01:25:58.679
of Kayi who battle in the frontiers
and stand against the orders of Ilkhanate.

851
01:25:59.040 --> 01:26:01.719
Take measures.

852
01:26:04.160 --> 01:26:06.919
How do you know that?

853
01:26:12.680 --> 01:26:15.519
I'm an alp of Karesi. my Bey.

854
01:26:16.440 --> 01:26:19.039
The sergeant of the alps.

855
01:26:24.000 --> 01:26:25.919
I'm offended that...

856
01:26:26.320 --> 01:26:29.959
my Beylic is desperate
against Ilkhanids for years.

857
01:26:30.160 --> 01:26:34.559
With your permission. I want to fight
for your cause and become a martyr.

858
01:26:49.240 --> 01:26:51.679
My soldiers!

859
01:26:52.120 --> 01:26:59.119
Our people suffered a lot in
Bursa because of Turks for years!

860
01:26:59.760 --> 01:27:04.519
Finally. it's time to
fight those barbarians...

861
01:27:04.760 --> 01:27:11.879
who attack and disgrace
the glory of Bursa like plague!

862
01:27:12.040 --> 01:27:16.759
Vengeance! Vengeance!

863
01:27:16.880 --> 01:27:21.159
Vengeance! Vengeance!

864
01:27:21.400 --> 01:27:23.719
For your wives!

865
01:27:23.840 --> 01:27:26.399
For Bursa!

866
01:27:28.280 --> 01:27:31.479
We will burn down
Sogut over them..

867
01:27:31.720 --> 01:27:34.479
And with God's help.

868
01:27:35.600 --> 01:27:44.279
we will enter the nest of those
barbarians and teach them a lesson finally!

869
01:27:47.520 --> 01:27:49.239
Soqgut.

870
01:27:49.480 --> 01:27:51.799
That's bad.

871
01:27:54.520 --> 01:28:00.119
Flaviu 1s waiting
for you in Sogut.

872
01:28:00.960 --> 01:28:04.719
May the victory be with you!

873
01:28:18.280 --> 01:28:20.999
Draw women and children
behind the outer walls.

874
01:28:21.040 --> 01:28:23.679
We'll take them out of
the city in case of an attack.

875
01:28:23.840 --> 01:28:27.679
Nobody wants to wait behind
in such times. Fatma Hatun.

876
01:28:28.760 --> 01:28:31.279
She's totally right.

877
01:28:31.920 --> 01:28:33.759
Yigit Bey.

878
01:28:34.120 --> 01:28:36.239
Are you alright? Why
did you leave bed?

879
01:28:36.480 --> 01:28:39.879
My cure isn't in the
healing house. Fatma Hatun.

880
01:28:42.800 --> 01:28:47.399
It's my duty. I need to place
my alps in the northern gate.

881
01:28:48.880 --> 01:28:52.039
Thank you for everything.

882
01:28:52.440 --> 01:28:54.319
I owe you a life.

883
01:28:54.640 --> 01:28:57.399
You sacrificed yourself
without hesitation.

884
01:28:59.120 --> 01:29:01.919
I would sacrifice a
thousand lives of mine.

885
01:29:02.960 --> 01:29:05.279
No problem.

886
01:29:08.760 --> 01:29:10.359
Sisters.

887
01:29:10.600 --> 01:29:12.159
No objections accepted

888
01:29:12.240 --> 01:29:16.039
I have to protect people for the sake
of Sheikh Edebali and Osman Bey.

889
01:29:16.080 --> 01:29:17.279
I can't risk them.

890
01:29:17.360 --> 01:29:19.919
Those who can't use any
weapons will be secured.

891
01:29:20.120 --> 01:29:22.319
Come on.

892
01:29:25.080 --> 01:29:26.879
Yigit Bey.

893
01:29:27.560 --> 01:29:30.479
You go assign your alps.

894
01:29:31.760 --> 01:29:35.759
We have spotted who
patrols and where. sir.

895
01:29:43.920 --> 01:29:46.919
We'll attack with
all our strength.

896
01:29:47.520 --> 01:29:50.519
However. Fatma
Hatun won't be harmed.

897
01:29:50.720 --> 01:29:52.279
I want her alive.

898
01:29:52.520 --> 01:29:54.799
For your information.

899
01:30:32.520 --> 01:30:34.999
Gonca. Didar! Hurry up!

900
01:30:35.160 --> 01:30:37.599
-Prepare the healing house!
-What's going on?

901
01:30:37.760 --> 01:30:40.679
Wait wait. What's
going on here? Clear the way!

902
01:30:44.240 --> 01:30:47.039
What's going on
here? Clear the way!

903
01:30:50.280 --> 01:30:51.879
My brothers! Who did this?

904
01:30:52.400 --> 01:30:55.799
Who did this?
Who did this to you?

905
01:30:56.080 --> 01:30:58.279
Temurtas.

906
01:30:58.720 --> 01:31:01.959
Yarhisar has fallen. my Bey.

907
01:31:05.880 --> 01:31:08.879
Forgive us my Bey.

908
01:31:11.600 --> 01:31:14.199
We couldn't protect our land.

909
01:31:14.560 --> 01:31:17.039
We couldn't save
our brothers. my Bey.

910
01:31:17.400 --> 01:31:20.359
-Forgive us.
-Temurtas...

911
01:31:20.840 --> 01:31:25.079
Temurtas!

912
01:31:26.240 --> 01:31:28.279
You will pay for this.

913
01:31:28.440 --> 01:31:31.799
You will pay for
this! You will pay

914
01:31:32.080 --> 01:31:34.599
Get your head up!

915
01:31:34.840 --> 01:31:38.359
Stop crying.
Stop crying. Alps!

916
01:31:38.440 --> 01:31:40.799
Prepare alps immediately!

917
01:31:41.120 --> 01:31:43.599
Prepare my horse!

918
01:31:43.840 --> 01:31:45.479
Son. son.

919
01:31:45.640 --> 01:31:49.679
There is nobody here to protect
the tribe. You can't send alps away.

920
01:31:49.680 --> 01:31:53.879
Are you pleased with the decision you
made about your brother. Alaeddin Bey?

921
01:31:53.920 --> 01:31:56.999
Mother. not now. Not now.

922
01:31:57.160 --> 01:31:58.559
Son.

923
01:31:59.000 --> 01:32:03.679
While we turn against each other. the
enemy can't wait to take our hearts out.

924
01:32:03.840 --> 01:32:06.559
You should take
a lesson from this.

925
01:32:06.720 --> 01:32:09.479
Mother. I understand you.

926
01:32:09.640 --> 01:32:12.279
I said not now. Not now.

927
01:32:12.520 --> 01:32:15.319
Prepare my horse immediately!

928
01:32:21.120 --> 01:32:25.959
When I look from here.
you seem so small.

929
01:32:29.160 --> 01:32:32.119
Enjoy the view. Saroz.

930
01:32:32.520 --> 01:32:35.599
This is the last time
you look down on me.

931
01:32:35.920 --> 01:32:38.319
Tomorrow. I will
look down on you.

932
01:32:38.440 --> 01:32:41.719
But you won't be
able to hear what I say.

933
01:32:41.920 --> 01:32:44.639
Because you will
be in the grave.

934
01:32:44.920 --> 01:32:52.999
Would you prefer us to attack with all our strength and
slaughter everyone in our way without mercy tomorrow...

935
01:32:53.240 --> 01:32:57.679
or would you surrender
tonight and save your lives?

936
01:32:58.360 --> 01:33:01.439
Oh Sahinshah...

937
01:33:02.200 --> 01:33:09.039
Well... When Boran Bey opened
the western gate for Orhan.

938
01:33:09.120 --> 01:33:12.999
you were looking inside
sitting 1n the woods. Remember?

939
01:33:13.200 --> 01:33:18.599
That's the only view you can
see in Bursa all along your lives.

940
01:33:19.040 --> 01:33:22.839
Tomorrow morning. you
will wake up with the sounds...

941
01:33:23.120 --> 01:33:27.199
of the stones our catapults
throw to hit your walls. Saroz.

942
01:33:27.480 --> 01:33:29.399
If you an sleep
tonight. of course.

943
01:33:29.600 --> 01:33:32.519
I cant of course.

944
01:33:32.920 --> 01:33:35.079
My commanders and
I will be discussing...

945
01:33:35.240 --> 01:33:42.399
which heads of yours should be sent to
which tribes. That's why I won't be sleeping.

946
01:33:44.920 --> 01:33:48.159
I will keep your head
in my horse's saddle...

947
01:33:48.320 --> 01:33:53.279
to make an example for people
In Iznik. Izmit and Constantinople.

948
01:33:53.480 --> 01:33:55.079
Oh..

949
01:33:58.600 --> 01:34:01.839
Come on. come on.

950
01:34:13.840 --> 01:34:17.879
Get prepared to go to
Sogut. We're leaving shortly.

951
01:34:30.880 --> 01:34:33.519
They are fighting us from
every direction Orhan.

952
01:34:33.840 --> 01:34:35.879
Who is attacking us?

953
01:34:36.400 --> 01:34:38.999
Nobody but Saroz.

954
01:34:39.280 --> 01:34:41.879
Let him do his best.

955
01:34:42.680 --> 01:34:45.319
Saroz isn't the only enemy.

956
01:34:46.040 --> 01:34:48.959
What about your exile?

957
01:34:50.040 --> 01:34:53.519
I got exiled. Nilufer.
I'm not a traitor.

958
01:35:17.720 --> 01:35:19.839
I'm starving to death.

959
01:35:20.160 --> 01:35:22.239
Why are they so late?

960
01:35:22.560 --> 01:35:26.279
They'll be back with
a sack of meat shortly.

961
01:35:26.760 --> 01:35:28.839
I hope they don't
kill all the animals.

962
01:35:29.160 --> 01:35:32.159
Perhaps. they will.

963
01:35:32.840 --> 01:35:36.319
I hope I won t die
of hunger until then.

964
01:35:38.400 --> 01:35:41.639
You should work
not blabber. Balaban.

965
01:35:41.960 --> 01:35:45.079
Pluck these. come on.

966
01:35:46.560 --> 01:35:48.599
We hunt.

967
01:35:48.880 --> 01:35:51.679
You cook.

968
01:35:51.920 --> 01:35:54.919
Well. you followed us up here.

969
01:35:55.080 --> 01:35:57.799
Feed the fire then.

970
01:35:58.120 --> 01:36:00.719
Bad hands make bad fire.

971
01:36:00.880 --> 01:36:03.239
Put a few more woods on it.

972
01:36:03.480 --> 01:36:06.999
So the meat will speak in fat.

973
01:36:07.600 --> 01:36:09.519
I'm glad you are here.

974
01:36:09.800 --> 01:36:15.239
If we stayed with Balaban. we
would be miserable. huh. Cerkutay?

975
01:36:15.440 --> 01:36:17.359
I don t care. brother.

976
01:36:17.520 --> 01:36:20.319
At this age of mine.

977
01:36:20.600 --> 01:36:24.559
someone will hunt.
pluck and serve me.

978
01:36:24.920 --> 01:36:29.559
The wound I got today didn't kill
me. but your words will. my Bey.

979
01:36:29.960 --> 01:36:32.679
Come on. we can't wait all day.

980
01:36:32.920 --> 01:36:36.999
Cook them fast. Or
we will eat them raw.

981
01:36:59.080 --> 01:37:01.799
Are you thinking about your son?

982
01:37:03.920 --> 01:37:06.479
It's been years. Cerkutay Bey.

983
01:37:08.120 --> 01:37:10.999
There is not a single day
when I do not think of him.

984
01:37:13.120 --> 01:37:17.039
Neither the pain has passed. nor
has the fire in my heart gone out.

985
01:37:17.600 --> 01:37:21.039
I remember that day as clear
as yesterday in my mind. Ayse!

986
01:37:21.120 --> 01:37:24.039
Ayse!

987
01:37:26.360 --> 01:37:29.279
Let my Hatun go.

988
01:37:30.000 --> 01:37:33.359
Let her go!

989
01:38:03.760 --> 01:38:06.519
Ayse!

990
01:38:12.440 --> 01:38:15.159
Halil... Ayse...

991
01:38:15.480 --> 01:38:16.799
Our son..

992
01:38:19.640 --> 01:38:22.719
Our son...

993
01:38:31.920 --> 01:38:35.119
It is as if the Byzantines
tore out my heart.

994
01:38:42.520 --> 01:38:44.319
We will find your son. my Halil.

995
01:38:44.400 --> 01:38:47.199
We checked everywhere.
we'll keep looking for him.

996
01:38:47.240 --> 01:38:50.599
Don't worry. Do
not lose your hope.

997
01:38:51.120 --> 01:38:54.719
-Right..
-I am always trying to be hopeful

998
01:38:59.120 --> 01:39:02.679
Tell me. What is the reason
for the fire in your heart?

999
01:39:04.400 --> 01:39:06.519
I cannot hold it in anymore.

1000
01:39:06.920 --> 01:39:09.039
Why are you accepting
all this. Orhan?

1001
01:39:09.280 --> 01:39:12.199
Why are you not saying
anything about Alaeddin's greed?

1002
01:39:12.320 --> 01:39:14.199
He is my brother.

1003
01:39:14.240 --> 01:39:18.399
Brothers support each other. They
do not draw their swords and fight.

1004
01:39:18.680 --> 01:39:20.479
Don t you see?

1005
01:39:20.560 --> 01:39:22.839
Alaeddin has lost his way.

1006
01:39:23.560 --> 01:39:25.999
Who lost his way. Nilufer Hatun?

1007
01:39:26.720 --> 01:39:29.199
Say it again.

1008
01:39:31.520 --> 01:39:35.839
I did everything for my brother.

1009
01:39:38.320 --> 01:39:41.399
What are you saying?

1010
01:39:50.320 --> 01:39:53.159
I am alright. I am...

1011
01:39:59.920 --> 01:40:02.839
-Was that all a game? -Right.

1012
01:40:03.040 --> 01:40:08.319
It was two brothers joining hands
and carrying the da'wah. Nilufer.

1013
01:40:08.760 --> 01:40:12.479
We wanted to seem weak so that
we could make our move secretly.

1014
01:40:16.280 --> 01:40:19.839
So you tricked us my Beys.

1015
01:40:20.120 --> 01:40:22.559
What are we going
to do now? Tell us that.

1016
01:40:22.640 --> 01:40:24.759
Let me tell you. Boran Bey.

1017
01:40:24.960 --> 01:40:27.079
Dumrul! Come here.

1018
01:40:27.160 --> 01:40:30.719
Come and give us the good news!

1019
01:40:32.040 --> 01:40:33.959
My Bey...

1020
01:40:34.080 --> 01:40:37.679
Thanks to Allah. I found
the entrance of the tunnel.

1021
01:40:37.840 --> 01:40:39.639
But I have bad news.

1022
01:40:39.880 --> 01:40:43.119
The soldiers coming out of
the tunnel will attack Sogut.

1023
01:40:43.520 --> 01:40:45.399
They won t be
able to do anything.

1024
01:40:45.400 --> 01:40:48.239
They will be defeated
and lose all their motivation.

1025
01:40:48.280 --> 01:40:52.839
Flavius will be left alone outside
once we explode the tunnel.

1026
01:40:53.880 --> 01:40:56.399
My Bey.. Why are we
going to explode the tunnel?

1027
01:40:56.440 --> 01:40:58.919
Why don't we go through
that tunnel and take Bursa?

1028
01:40:58.960 --> 01:41:01.999
We can enter the tunnel. but
we may not be able to leave it.

1029
01:41:02.080 --> 01:41:03.039
It's full of traps.

1030
01:41:03.080 --> 01:41:07.599
If we enter that tunnel. they will close the
entrance behind us. And we will lose all our alps.

1031
01:41:07.640 --> 01:41:13.079
Brother... Temurtas saw this as an
opportunity and attacked Yarhisar.

1032
01:41:13.800 --> 01:41:16.239
He took control of the castle.

1033
01:41:16.600 --> 01:41:18.559
Temurtas can wait.

1034
01:41:18.680 --> 01:41:22.239
We never gave up on
our promises or revenge.

1035
01:41:22.320 --> 01:41:25.799
We will go and explode the
tunnel which is Bursa's life support.

1036
01:41:26.040 --> 01:41:29.399
-You will go to the headquarters..
-And stop Sahinshah Bey.

1037
01:41:29.440 --> 01:41:32.079
Thanks to my Allah!

1038
01:41:32.240 --> 01:41:34.519
Like old days. huh?

1039
01:41:34.720 --> 01:41:37.879
Two hearts and one
mind joined hands...

1040
01:41:38.000 --> 01:41:41.479
Who can stop us now?

1041
01:41:41.960 --> 01:41:45.079
Now this war is not the
war of hunger and fullness.

1042
01:41:45.560 --> 01:41:47.959
This is the war of existence.

1043
01:41:49.000 --> 01:41:50.959
Now listen to me carefully.

1044
01:41:51.720 --> 01:41:56.279
Dumrul. Balaban. You
will surround the tunnel.

1045
01:41:58.880 --> 01:42:01.639
Balaban. go to the other side!

1046
01:42:07.200 --> 01:42:11.599
Before we approach the tunnel. the
area around it will be full of soldiers.

1047
01:42:12.680 --> 01:42:14.679
AbdurRahman. Kanturali.

1048
01:42:14.680 --> 01:42:18.399
You will infiltrate from the
front. You will be so quiet that...

1049
01:42:18.520 --> 01:42:23.359
th only thing they feel
will be the bitter face of death.

1050
01:42:42.640 --> 01:42:43.879
My Orhan Bey...

1051
01:42:43.920 --> 01:42:53.799
How are we going to approach this tunnel.
which is Bursa's life support. with a
huge cart without letting anyone see us?

1052
01:42:54.040 --> 01:42:58.719
We have no one who can do that
better than you and Cerkutay Bey.

1053
01:42:59.800 --> 01:43:03.439
EyvAllah.

1054
01:43:12.960 --> 01:43:15.079
Who are they?

1055
01:43:15.560 --> 01:43:17.599
We brought fresh fruits to you.

1056
01:43:17.800 --> 01:43:21.439
-Go away. -But...

1057
01:43:24.400 --> 01:43:27.319
We cannot

1058
01:43:27.960 --> 01:43:30.959
From now on. wherever we go...

1059
01:43:31.080 --> 01:43:33.919
all doors will
lead us to Bursa.

1060
01:43:37.240 --> 01:43:41.199
Ambush!

1061
01:44:12.560 --> 01:44:15.039
Then we will enter the
tunnel. huh. my Bey?

1062
01:44:15.080 --> 01:44:17.919
That's what the enemy
wants you to think. Kantural.

1063
01:44:17.920 --> 01:44:20.639
Do not think that they will
leave the scorpion's nest empty.

1064
01:44:20.680 --> 01:44:24.599
But you will make
them get out of that hole.

1065
01:44:27.680 --> 01:44:30.959
-AbdurRahman. -Kantural!

1066
01:46:50.840 --> 01:46:53.679
Come on Alps! Carry the
Greek fire into the tunnel!

1067
01:46:53.800 --> 01:46:58.199
Now it is time to stamp Kayi's seal
onto the nest of demons! Come on!

1068
01:47:20.480 --> 01:47:24.839
Sogut is in the
hands of Flavius.

1069
01:47:25.720 --> 01:47:27.999
And Sahinshah ..

1070
01:47:28.240 --> 01:47:32.039
Will be in our hands.

1071
01:47:34.520 --> 01:47:40.959
We will inflict a defeat on him that is much
greater than the one we made Orhan experience.

1072
01:47:41.320 --> 01:47:45.079
Soldiers! Set
traps on the walls!

1073
01:47:45.200 --> 01:47:50.439
Pile up the tar. the Greek
fire. everything we have!

1074
01:47:50.680 --> 01:47:53.879
-As you order Lord Saroz.
-Go now.

1075
01:47:54.360 --> 01:47:58.759
Sir! Turks are coming!
They found the tunnel!

1076
01:47:59.560 --> 01:48:02.119
Damn it.

1077
01:48:02.560 --> 01:48:05.159
Damn it.

1078
01:48:05.360 --> 01:48:09.759
Orhan.. I will bury
you in that tunnel!

1079
01:48:22.840 --> 01:48:26.079
Come on Dursun
Stop wasting time!

1080
01:48:27.000 --> 01:48:29.199
I am the one who
carries everything here!

1081
01:48:29.240 --> 01:48:30.319
This is the last one.

1082
01:48:30.320 --> 01:48:33.879
We are walking on a difficult road. You should
go back if you are going to complain like that.

1083
01:48:33.880 --> 01:48:35.679
Then who will do your work?

1084
01:48:37.120 --> 01:48:40.999
Run! Do not let them advance!

1085
01:48:41.200 --> 01:48:43.679
-Run!
-They are coming!

1086
01:48:43.760 --> 01:48:47.119
They will regret coming
here. Come on! Let's go.

1087
01:48:55.000 --> 01:48:58.439
-Brother! Brother. they are coming!
-Come on!

1088
01:49:07.560 --> 01:49:09.279
Hide!

1089
01:49:09.440 --> 01:49:12.559
Come her. Get down!

1090
01:49:35.720 --> 01:49:40.279
Now only one step remains to
the border my father wants to draw.

1091
01:49:40.760 --> 01:49:43.799
Boran. Cerkutay.
You will go to Sogut.

1092
01:49:44.080 --> 01:49:46.839
Flavius must be outside.
We must find out where he is.

1093
01:49:46.920 --> 01:49:50.199
Halime. Dursun. Nilufer.
You go back to the tribe.

1094
01:49:50.720 --> 01:49:54.639
Kara Halil. We are
going to the headquarters.

1095
01:49:55.520 --> 01:49:58.039
Come on!

1096
01:50:10.600 --> 01:50:13.519
Give me some water. Alp Tekin!

1097
01:50:22.760 --> 01:50:25.519
EyvAllah.

1098
01:50:29.360 --> 01:50:33.559
The catapults are ready. my Bey.
The cannonballs are also ready. my Bey!

1099
01:50:35.480 --> 01:50:40.119
Our glorious sanjak will
fly over the towers of Bursa.

1100
01:51:09.000 --> 01:51:12.519
Welcome. Alaeddin Bey.

1101
01:51:12.760 --> 01:51:16.999
Your presence here
will strengthen us!

1102
01:51:17.280 --> 01:51:20.159
Thank you. Sahinshah Bey.

1103
01:51:22.080 --> 01:51:24.799
You will give the good
news to my Osman Bey.

1104
01:51:25.560 --> 01:51:28.719
Now no one can
stand in your way!

1105
01:51:29.560 --> 01:51:34.199
There will be no
war Sahinshah Bey.

1106
01:51:37.000 --> 01:51:38.519
It's over now.

1107
01:51:38.880 --> 01:51:43.159
You no longer have any
authority over the Alps.

1108
01:52:18.120 --> 01:52:21.559
The captivity that has
lasted for years in Bursa.

1109
01:52:26.600 --> 01:52:30.599
Turks must pay the price
of this in Sogut today.

1110
01:52:34.880 --> 01:52:37.239
Commander Flavius!

1111
01:52:40.280 --> 01:52:42.319
Orhan..

1112
01:52:42.880 --> 01:52:47.519
They found the tunnel in
Bursa. They blew the tunnel up!

1113
01:53:01.480 --> 01:53:04.519
-Sir. there is one more thing.
-What is it?!

1114
01:53:04.760 --> 01:53:07.599
They also sent
reinforcement units to Sogut.

1115
01:53:29.800 --> 01:53:32.679
What are you saying. Alaeddin?

1116
01:53:33.280 --> 01:53:36.359
You heard me
well. Sahinshah Bey.

1117
01:53:36.560 --> 01:53:40.079
Not a single Alp will
take another step.

1118
01:53:41.960 --> 01:53:46.119
You are making a mistake.
Orhan must have manipulated you.

1119
01:53:46.240 --> 01:53:48.719
You are missing a
great chance. Alaeddin!

1120
01:53:48.800 --> 01:53:50.199
Use your mind!

1121
01:53:50.320 --> 01:53:52.839
I always...

1122
01:53:52.920 --> 01:53:55.639
use my mind and
wisdom. Sahinshah Bey!

1123
01:53:55.760 --> 01:54:00.479
I am not doing anything for the
chair. I do everything for our homeland!

1124
01:54:00.560 --> 01:54:02.599
You lost the right
way. Alaeddin.

1125
01:54:02.800 --> 01:54:06.399
This de ision will
make you regret!

1126
01:54:09.240 --> 01:54:11.599
I am not responding
to the things you said.

1127
01:54:11.640 --> 01:54:14.599
Because you have
the love of gaza in you.

1128
01:54:14.640 --> 01:54:18.799
But.. My patience
also has a limit

1129
01:54:19.000 --> 01:54:21.199
Know that.

1130
01:54:22.600 --> 01:54:25.999
I supported you for no reason!

1131
01:54:26.360 --> 01:54:30.359
From now on. you are all alone!

1132
01:55:10.840 --> 01:55:13.559
The tunnel is closed.

1133
01:55:14.280 --> 01:55:17.679
I don't know if Saroz
is dead or alive!

1134
01:55:17.760 --> 01:55:21.079
They ruined our most
important defense!

1135
01:55:29.760 --> 01:55:32.799
So Orhan was
playing a game and..

1136
01:55:32.920 --> 01:55:36.399
Gaining strength.

1137
01:55:36.560 --> 01:55:40.439
But he won't be able to
find a chance like this again.

1138
01:55:41.520 --> 01:55:44.519
That was the only way to Bursa!

1139
01:55:44.600 --> 01:55:48.759
You made a mistake by
letting Orhan speak. Temurtas!

1140
01:55:49.080 --> 01:55:51.479
For Orhan...

1141
01:55:51.960 --> 01:55:55.119
even death will
be a reward. Flavius.

1142
01:55:55.240 --> 01:55:57.719
Look. Temurtas.

1143
01:55:58.280 --> 01:56:00.679
Bursa won t fall.

1144
01:56:01.200 --> 01:56:05.719
And you will help me!

1145
01:56:11.520 --> 01:56:15.399
While Orhan is
dreaming of an attack...

1146
01:56:15.680 --> 01:56:18.639
we will do
such a thing that...

1147
01:56:18.760 --> 01:56:23.999
he won't even have the
chance to defend himself.

1148
01:56:29.360 --> 01:56:31.359
I assure you.

1149
01:56:46.200 --> 01:56:49.359
Don't do that again. brother
even if it was a game...

1150
01:56:49.480 --> 01:56:53.319
I felt different when we
raised our voices and had a fight.

1151
01:56:53.440 --> 01:56:54.919
Don't say that...

1152
01:56:55.040 --> 01:56:57.719
Everyone was saying
There is no Orhan now...

1153
01:56:57.960 --> 01:57:00.359
Look. there is no
tunnel in Bursa now.

1154
01:57:01.720 --> 01:57:06.199
You exploded Bursa's
life support. brother!

1155
01:57:22.960 --> 01:57:25.479
Welcome. my Bey.

1156
01:57:26.000 --> 01:57:28.559
Welcome. father.

1157
01:57:29.360 --> 01:57:31.399
Tell me...

1158
01:57:31.720 --> 01:57:34.959
Who are these
people greeting me?

1159
01:57:35.040 --> 01:57:41.359
Are these the sons I trusted and handed
over my Beylic. my army. and my seal to?

1160
01:57:41.760 --> 01:57:48.719
Or the sons who do not listen
to me and disobey my orders?

1161
01:57:48.920 --> 01:57:50.399
Why do you say that. father?

1162
01:57:50.760 --> 01:57:53.639
Our only goal is to make
conquests on your way.

1163
01:57:53.800 --> 01:57:54.919
And to conquer Bursa.

1164
01:57:55.040 --> 01:57:58.719
Bursa is now closer to us
than ever before. my Bey.

1165
01:57:59.120 --> 01:58:02.079
Where Bursa stands...

1166
01:58:02.120 --> 01:58:03.799
Is not the matter!

1167
01:58:04.040 --> 01:58:06.199
Where do you stand?

1168
01:58:06.400 --> 01:58:09.599
By my side or against me?!

1169
01:58:10.200 --> 01:58:17.039
Is there any explanation for your stubbornness
and rebellion against my order. Orhan?

1170
01:58:17.160 --> 01:58:19.159
What about you Alaeddin?

1171
01:58:19.360 --> 01:58:24.639
Is there an explanation for dismissing
the commander I appointed from his duty?

1172
01:58:25.320 --> 01:58:27.239
There is. my Bey.

1173
01:58:27.480 --> 01:58:29.959
I am responsible for that.

1174
01:58:31.440 --> 01:58:35.639
Your brother says that he s
responsible for that. Alaeddin.

1175
01:58:36.000 --> 01:58:41.159
Tell me. Did he force you
to be part of this game?

1176
01:58:41.320 --> 01:58:46.479
Never. father. We did everything
together with my brother.

1177
01:58:46.840 --> 01:58:50.759
I am responsible
as much as he is.

1178
01:58:52.520 --> 01:58:55.519
We did everything
for the future of Kayi...

1179
01:58:55.840 --> 01:58:59.479
for the safety of the road of
conquest you opened. my Bey.

1180
01:58:59.640 --> 01:59:03.319
We did everything as
you taught us. my Bey.

1181
01:59:03.840 --> 01:59:06.159
We did not give
up on the right way.

1182
01:59:07.000 --> 01:59:11.159
I taught you how to
walk on the right path.

1183
01:59:11.360 --> 01:59:14.279
Not how to stray from the path.

1184
01:59:16.960 --> 01:59:20.639
The enemies had united and had
been coming at us from all sides. my Bey.

1185
01:59:20.960 --> 01:59:24.959
If we started marching to Bursa.
they would kill everyone in our tribe...

1186
01:59:25.200 --> 01:59:28.919
Sogut and many other lands.
They would make our people suffer.

1187
01:59:29.240 --> 01:59:32.919
But we ruined their cooperation
as two brothers. my Bey.

1188
01:59:33.160 --> 01:59:37.359
That oppressor called Saroz is now
captivated behind the walls of Bursa. my Bey.

1189
01:59:37.800 --> 01:59:40.119
We destroyed the
game of the devil.

1190
01:59:40.200 --> 01:59:43.759
You decide if we made a mistake.
We are ready for the punishment.

1191
01:59:43.880 --> 01:59:45.799
Obviously. you
don't agree with us.

1192
01:59:45.920 --> 01:59:48.919
You are wrong. Orhan.

1193
01:59:58.320 --> 02:00:02.439
I totally agree with you.

1194
02:00:10.400 --> 02:00:15.519
I just wanted to
hear it from you.

1195
02:00:18.280 --> 02:00:22.479
A crooked sword rusts
in the sheath. sons.

1196
02:00:22.840 --> 02:00:29.239
You swung your swords
straight for the good of the state.

1197
02:00:29.560 --> 02:00:35.759
You never abandoned the path
which I thought was right and taught you.

1198
02:00:36.840 --> 02:00:41.119
You succeeded
together as united.

1199
02:00:46.920 --> 02:00:51.439
Oh father... Will
your tests ever end?

1200
02:00:52.520 --> 02:00:56.359
My own test hasn t
even ended. sons.

1201
02:00:57.600 --> 02:01:02.359
Our ghazis and martyrs should be sure that
they sacrificed their blood for a reason.

1202
02:01:02.600 --> 02:01:04.719
Bursa will be a
property of Kayi.

1203
02:01:05.040 --> 02:01:06.799
InshaAllah.

1204
02:01:07.040 --> 02:01:09.559
What are you waiting for then?

1205
02:01:09.760 --> 02:01:14.039
The dark steel shall have
the blood of the cruel now.

1206
02:01:14.520 --> 02:01:17.359
Raise your swords for Allah.

1207
02:01:17.520 --> 02:01:20.919
And lower them with the breath
of our Mighty Prophet (PBUH).

1208
02:01:21.200 --> 02:01:23.119
Go beyond those walls...

1209
02:01:23.280 --> 02:01:26.199
and capture Bursa.

1210
02:01:26.560 --> 02:01:28.159
I can feel it.

1211
02:01:28.400 --> 02:01:32.879
Bursa is closer than
even one step now.

1212
02:01:34.960 --> 02:01:38.399
Allahu akbar!
Allahu akbar!

1213
02:01:38.600 --> 02:01:42.799
Allahu akbar! Allahu akbar!

1214
02:02:11.320 --> 02:02:14.559
What a tough test
this is. white-maned.

1215
02:02:15.480 --> 02:02:18.519
You have been my
companion for a long time.

1216
02:02:19.920 --> 02:02:22.479
You carry my
troubles. white-maned.

1217
02:02:22.760 --> 02:02:24.679
Tell me.

1218
02:02:25.600 --> 02:02:32.879
How hard is the test of having
the desire to own the throne...

1219
02:02:33.000 --> 02:02:36.799
which turns brothers against
each other and sons against fathers?

1220
02:02:39.000 --> 02:02:41.639
With Allah's help.

1221
02:02:41.840 --> 02:02:44.399
we found peace.

1222
02:02:45.440 --> 02:02:49.839
Are we making all these
efforts to sit on that throne?

1223
02:02:53.800 --> 02:02:56.799
If it is so. I don't want it.

1224
02:02:57.400 --> 02:03:01.839
May Allah take my life but not let me
disgrace myself for this mortal world.

1225
02:03:02.840 --> 02:03:05.999
May He keep me away
from the devil's traps.

1226
02:03:10.320 --> 02:03:12.959
Well. white-maned...

1227
02:03:13.320 --> 02:03:16.759
There are crazy foals
galloping in my blood.

1228
02:03:20.200 --> 02:03:23.479
Wait! Don't be so jealous!

1229
02:03:26.640 --> 02:03:29.639
They are just In my veins.

1230
02:03:36.920 --> 02:03:39.999
Taking me from one
dream to another.

1231
02:03:41.160 --> 02:03:44.519
I want this
suffering to end now.

1232
02:03:45.160 --> 02:03:48.239
This land shall be ours.

1233
02:03:48.720 --> 02:03:51.679
New realms shall meet our flag.

1234
02:03:52.040 --> 02:03:55.119
The azan of Mohammad
(PBUH) shall be heard there too.

1235
02:03:59.440 --> 02:04:01.959
I mean. white-maned...

1236
02:04:03.440 --> 02:04:07.359
There 1s a never dying
fire of conquest inside me.

1237
02:04:23.880 --> 02:04:25.839
Come here.

1238
02:04:26.360 --> 02:04:27.719
Come.

1239
02:06:16.280 --> 02:06:20.079
-Selamun Aleykum.
-Aleykum Selam.

1240
02:06:26.120 --> 02:06:28.039
You are?

1241
02:06:28.560 --> 02:06:32.799
We are one of those who say the
land vanishes. but the morals stay.

1242
02:06:33.360 --> 02:06:36.799
As long as the
blue sky doesn't fall.

1243
02:06:37.360 --> 02:06:40.919
as long as the sohd
ground doesn t collapse

1244
02:06:41.200 --> 02:06:45.119
who can break
your morals? We say.

1245
02:06:46.160 --> 02:06:52.239
We hide our presence in absence
and hide our absence in presence.

1246
02:06:57.840 --> 02:07:00.439
EyvAllah.

1247
02:07:03.880 --> 02:07:08.639
I'm pleased and honored.

1248
02:07:10.080 --> 02:07:11.999
But...

1249
02:07:12.600 --> 02:07:18.039
If you are so
secret and ancient.

1250
02:07:21.000 --> 02:07:23.319
I have a question.

1251
02:07:23.720 --> 02:07:27.039
Why is Turkistan
in this situation?

1252
02:07:32.000 --> 02:07:35.279
Why is the Islam
world in this situation?

1253
02:07:41.960 --> 02:07:44.559
You couldn't capture
the castle of Bursa.

1254
02:07:45.000 --> 02:07:47.879
You couldn't perform
an all-out attack.

1255
02:07:48.160 --> 02:07:50.679
When they ask you why.

1256
02:07:50.920 --> 02:07:54.239
you say you don't want
to destroy the city of Bursa.

1257
02:07:56.880 --> 02:07:58.479
Tell me.

1258
02:07:58.760 --> 02:08:04.799
Which one is harder? Rebuilding
Bursa or the grief of losing it?

1259
02:08:08.120 --> 02:08:11.719
What kind of leadership
is this. Osman Bey's son?

1260
02:08:17.360 --> 02:08:21.799
Deep inside me. I asked
myself this question.

1261
02:08:24.800 --> 02:08:28.959
I suffered for days and
nights with this question.

1262
02:08:31.280 --> 02:08:33.799
I watched the time.

1263
02:08:34.480 --> 02:08:36.319
And I thought..

1264
02:08:36.680 --> 02:08:40.279
Where is Genghis Khan who
owned the half of the world?

1265
02:08:40.640 --> 02:08:46.359
He demolished many castles. took
many lives. destroyed many cities.

1266
02:08:47.120 --> 02:08:51.199
He smashed the world
of Turks and Islam.

1267
02:08:53.680 --> 02:08:56.479
But now...

1268
02:08:57.080 --> 02:09:00.279
his ancestors became Muslims.

1269
02:09:00.840 --> 02:09:03.039
They got defeated
by their enemy.

1270
02:09:03.280 --> 02:09:07.799
In this era while
our state is smashed.

1271
02:09:08.120 --> 02:09:11.239
we should make a decision.

1272
02:09:13.640 --> 02:09:16.879
We will either have a state
to survive over centuries...

1273
02:09:17.200 --> 02:09:21.799
or become like our enemy
in the end like they did.

1274
02:09:24.280 --> 02:09:29.559
How is the conquest
of Bursa related to this?

1275
02:09:29.640 --> 02:09:34.479
Since the battle of Malazgirt. we have been
working to make these lands a homeland for us.

1276
02:09:34.560 --> 02:09:37.799
Crusaders and
Mongolians keep coming.

1277
02:09:38.120 --> 02:09:41.719
We never could go beyond Bursa.

1278
02:09:41.960 --> 02:09:45.479
Bursa is the last
castle for Byzantine.

1279
02:09:45.680 --> 02:09:49.839
For us. its a
bridge to carry us...

1280
02:09:50.200 --> 02:09:53.319
to Constantinople
and Rumelia.

1281
02:09:54.120 --> 02:09:59.239
After we choke and capture Bursa. we should
perform new attacks without wasting time.

1282
02:10:00.480 --> 02:10:04.359
Greek people should
take our side completely.

1283
02:10:05.640 --> 02:10:09.799
And this depends on how we
treat them during the conquest.

1284
02:10:10.200 --> 02:10:15.199
I don't want to leave a terrible story
for them to tell their grandchildren.

1285
02:10:16.840 --> 02:10:20.599
They should be the
children of our state too.

1286
02:10:22.400 --> 02:10:25.599
And all the other nations
seeing how we treat them...

1287
02:10:25.760 --> 02:10:29.079
shall take shelter
in our country.

1288
02:10:34.280 --> 02:10:38.439
How about the condition of
Turkmen Beys in Anatolia?

1289
02:10:38.800 --> 02:10:42.399
We scattered when the
Seljuk State collapsed.

1290
02:10:42.720 --> 02:10:46.559
Our nation are looking
for the new reat leader.

1291
02:10:47.280 --> 02:10:50.719
Turks are a
leader-centered nation.

1292
02:10:51.000 --> 02:10:55.319
Who will be the new leader?

1293
02:10:56.000 --> 02:11:02.799
Kayi. Germiyan.
Mentesogullari or Karaman?

1294
02:11:04.120 --> 02:11:07.119
It seems everyone wants
to take over the mission.

1295
02:11:07.440 --> 02:11:09.679
Time will show us.

1296
02:11:10.000 --> 02:11:15.599
But I'm ready to take over the mission
as Orhan Bey. son of Osman Bey.

1297
02:11:17.280 --> 02:11:21.399
The new state of Turks.
Islam and all the humans...

1298
02:11:21.560 --> 02:11:23.919
should be Osman Bey's state.

1299
02:11:24.080 --> 02:11:28.079
I would sacrifice my life
and blood for this cause.

1300
02:11:29.520 --> 02:11:33.399
History is made by
the brave. the devoted...

1301
02:11:33.560 --> 02:11:36.359
and those who take action.

1302
02:11:41.120 --> 02:11:44.879
I'm glad to hear that.

1303
02:11:48.160 --> 02:11:50.759
May Allah help you.

1304
02:11:51.000 --> 02:11:53.919
Now that you are ready.

1305
02:11:54.080 --> 02:11:58.159
we will give
you three secrets.

1306
02:11:58.440 --> 02:12:00.679
And one gift.

1307
02:12:01.160 --> 02:12:05.279
Will you keep the
secrets and the gift?

1308
02:12:05.800 --> 02:12:09.439
Whose secrets? Whose gift?

1309
02:12:10.160 --> 02:12:14.839
The secret and the gift given to
the heroes you see in your dreams.

1310
02:13:00.560 --> 02:13:01.479
Now...

1311
02:13:02.040 --> 02:13:06.679
Are you ready to
keep the secrets. son?

1311
